Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Welcome to your dream home in Milton.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.94,0:00:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Step inside and feel the grandeur unfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Look up at that stunning 37-ft domed ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.84,0:00:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}It sets a breathtaking tone for the space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.79,0:00:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}As we move forward, notice the elegance throughout.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}11-ft ceilings create an airy ambiance on the main floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Every corner showcases exquisite crown molding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The warmth of hardwood flooring invites you further.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Here’s the heart of the home, the modern kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Equipped with top-of-the-line JennAir appliances.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The Titanium Leather-finish countertop is simply striking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.42,0:00:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}And don’t miss the spice kitchen for culinary adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.37,0:00:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Imagine entertaining with ease in this walk-in pantry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.32,0:00:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Now let&apos;s cozy up in the family room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The gas fireplace brings warmth and comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.21,0:00:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Perfect for relaxing evenings with loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Next, we step into the formal living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}A sophisticated space for gatherings and celebrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}The dining room awaits, ready for dinner parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Every detail in this home tells a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Thank you for joining me on this wonderful tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}I hope you felt the love in every room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}This could be your perfect escape in the countryside.
